CIVILWISE SERVICES INC.
1240 E. STATE STREET
SUITE 101
PAHRUMP, NV 89048
775-751-1413
NOTICE OF LIEN
DOC # 955097
Official Records Nye County Nevada
Deborah Beatty - Recorder
05/11/2021 10:04:04 AM
Requested By: CIVILWISE
RPTT : $0
Recorded By: to
Recording Fee:
$37.00
Page 1 of 1
NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN THAT:
The undersigned claims a lien upon the property described in this notice for work, materials or
equipment furnished or to be furnished for the improvement of the property:
1. The amount of the original contract is: $37,000.00
2. The total amount of all additional or changed work, materials and equipment, if any, is: $0.0
3. The total amount of all payments received to date is: $18,500.00
4. The total amount of the lien, after deducting all just credits and offsets, is: $18,500.00
5. The name of the owner, if known, of the property is: Oakridge Enterprises, LLC
6. The name of the person by whom the lien claimant was employed or to whom the lien claimant
furnished or agreed to furnish work, materials or equipment is: Top Rank Builders
7. A brief statement of the terms of payment of the lien claimant's contract is: "Client shall, upon
receipt of a partial or full invoice, pay CIVILWISE for services furnished."
8. A description of the property to be charged with the lien is: 3.78 acres in NE 1/4 of Sec 12,
Township 21 South, Range 53 East, M.D.M F#277119, Parcel 1
Company Name: Civilwise Services Inc.
Address: 1240 E. State Street, Suite 101, Pahrump, NV 89048
David A. Richards, President-Civilwise Services, Inc
State of Nevada
County of Nye
On May 11, 2021
personally appeared before me, a Notary Public in and
for said County and State, DAUD H. RICHARDS , who acknowledged to me that
he executed the same.
WITNESS my hand and official seal.
borat Q Malling
Signature of Notary Officer
DEBORAH J. MALLORY
Notary Public, State of Nevada
Appointment No. 13-12201-1
My Appt. Expires Nov 10, 2021
